  "title": "Petrol Station Pump Attendant",
  "description": "<p><strong>📍 Location: Islandwide </strong></p>\n<p><strong>📌 Position : Pump Attendant ⛽</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Salary:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>- Full-Time: $1700 - $1,800</strong></p>\n<p><strong>- Part-Time: $10 - $11/hr</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet customers in a friendly and courteous manner</li>\n  <li>Provide customers with information about fuel products and other services</li>\n  <li>Handle all cash and credit transactions accurately</li>\n  <li>Check fluid levels and tire pressures</li>\n  <li>Refuel vehicles</li>\n  <li>Clean windscreens</li>\n  <li>Collect payments and issue receipts</li>\n  <li>Carry out basic vehicle checks</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 19C9611</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Reg No: R1433735 Teng Wei Mun (Celest)</p>",
